Package: seq.cda
Title: Sequential Causal Decomposition Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Suyeon", "Kim", , "skim733@ucr.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:  Provides tools for sequential causal decomposition analysis with
    two time-ordered intervention targets. The package supports estimation of
    disparity reduction and disparity remaining under static and stochastic
    interventions for researchers studying group disparities.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
